channel.title: Does anyone still have the original, still-obfuscated 317 client?
channel.description:
Hi, I'd like to try my hand at deobfuscating r317 myself. I can't find an original client anywhere, only deobfuscated ones. I'm wondering if anyone here happens to still have the obfuscated original client.
I popped on IRC and was told to post it here. Thanks, and if you don't have it, it's okay. It's just something I'd like to have sometime, and I know the deobfuscated version is superior. I just want to try it myself.
